      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING VICTORIA (7) recorded her 2nd career win last time at Richmond, scoring by a neck (29.82). Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Great chance to get the job done again. AMAZING MOLLY (8) has been freshened since recording her maiden success last time by a nose at this track over 340m (20.12). Will break from a wide draw. Has placed three times at this track. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. HAND ME DOWN (1) stalked the lead from a low draw and fought on well to finish 4 lengths back in second (30.79) at this track in a Mix over 527m. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and three minor placings from four starts. Can measure up. RADETZKY MARCH (6) has top-three claims while fresh from a eight weeks break.",
